OL,5, The prices of fridges, freezers and    
OL,6, dishwashers are up by a third since    
OL,7, last year and set to climb higher, the 
OL,8, boss of a white goods retailer says.   
OL,10,FNick Glynne from Buy It Direct, which  
OL,11,Fowns Appliances Direct, blamed Covid   
OL,12,Flockdowns in China, shortages of       
OL,13,Fmaterials and sky-high shipping costs. 
OL,15,FAmdea, a UK appliance maker trade      
OL,16,Fassociation, said wholesale prices had 
OL,17,Frisen by nine per cent in three months.
OL,19,FRetailers AO World and Currys also said
OL,20,Ftheir prices had been impacted.        
